{
  "v": 1,
  "_comment": "TypeScript / JavaScript template (Vite / Next / Node library \u2014 pnpm, npm, yarn). pnpm|npm|yarn install-family is ask (mutates node_modules + lockfile); test / build / lint / tsc are allow; npx / pnpm dlx / yarn dlx are ask because they download and execute arbitrary npm packages. Shlex-prefix note: Bash(pnpm) alone would match every pnpm subcommand, so we enumerate explicit safe subcommands.",
